Invocation Name: get fit
des:
This exercise routine is to be performed 3 times per week, with at least a day rest in between each working day. Beginners will need very simple equipment; an exercise mat and a pair of light dumbbells will do. The workouts are simple to follow, and are meant to be performed with moderate intensity. Beginners will see results within a month of consistent training in terms of strength, cardiovascular performance, and energy levels.
